        <dd>Anyone registered and logged in, either as a Master or a Sub‑user.</dd>
        <dt>“Master”</dt>
        <dd>The primary account holder with full permissions, able to manage sub‑users, products, and settings.</dd>
        <dt>“Sub‑user”</dt>
        <dd>An additional account under the same Master, with restricted access to routes as configured by the Master.</dd>
        <dt>“Content”</dt>
        <dd>All data entered or uploaded by Users, including products, batches, sales records, expenses, and employee reports.</dd>
