      <p>We may suspend or terminate your access if you violate these Terms or fail to maintain an active subscription. You may request data deletion at any time; complete removal occurs within 30 days.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>9. Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p>We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time. The “Last updated” date will reflect changes. Continued use after modifications constitutes acceptance.</p>
